orms) But what does a wizard have. What defines them to where there can be no question can be asked of what our primary specilaty is. We are supposed to be (in theory) masters of magical damage and deffence. I'm not even going to go into the magical defence talks, for we arnt even the master of the formost said magical damage. That is a wizards main gripe. If it seems we bash other classes, i dont think we are, we are simply comparing. If we seem to be bashing, im sure everyone agrees that we apologize to the others, specialy other int casters. <br>
